articles.title: Czechs stun 10-man Dutch to seal Euro quarterfinal berth - SuperSport
articles.description: Striker Patrik Schick scored his fourth goal of the tournament as the Czech Republic stunned 10-man Netherlands with a deserved 2-0 victory in their European Championship last-16 clash.

articles.author: Gerard Couzens
articles.title: Three British men are caught in mid-Atlantic with £80m TON of cocaine on yacht - Daily Mail
articles.description: Three British men were arrested in the mid-Atlantic by Spanish police after a ton of cocaine was discovered on a yacht sailing from the Caribbean to Europe on June 13.
articles.content: Three British men have been arrested in the mid-Atlantic by Spanish police and Customs agents after a ton of cocaine worth more than £80million was discovered on a yacht sailing from the Caribbean to… [+4942 chars]
